                    <l n="645">exitu diro temerata ponti</l>
                    <l n="646">iura piavit. </l>
                    <l n="647">exigit poenas mare provocatum:</l>
                    <l n="648">Tiphys in primis, domitor profundi,</l>
                    <l n="649">liquit indocto regimen magistro;</l>
                    <l n="650">litore externo, procul a paternis</l>
                    <l n="651">occidens regnis tumuloque vili </l>
                    <l n="652">tectus ignotas iacet inter umbras.</l>
